  <brief_title>Laparoscopic Gastric Bypass as Metabolic Surgery in Obesity Class 1</brief_title>
  <official_title>Gastric Bypass as Metabolic Surgery in Obesity Class 1: a Prospective Study of the Short, Mid and Long Term Results Among Mexicans</official_title>
