  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective study including Mexican patients diagnosed with type 2 diabetes and class 1&#xD;
      obesity, undergoing laparoscopic gastric bypass. The objective was to determine short,&#xD;
      mid-and long-term outcomes (weight loss, metabolic, morbidity and diabetes remission). A&#xD;
      subanalysis was included, based on preoperative usage of one (Group A) or more antidiabetics&#xD;
      ± insulin (Group B).&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
